      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source of parts. The exterior has sustained significant wear, including several deep rust spots on the rocker panels, a cracked windshield, and a large dent in the rear passenger door. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul as it currently struggles to idle and leaks oil consistently. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the fabric and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
