    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is a diamond in the rough and ready for some TLC! While it currently shows significant wear and will need mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a solid foundation for anyone who loves to restore cars to their former glory. It's a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel of this model and make it your own!",
